<br>
Things are better, yes. I am pleased, yes. But this is nothing like excessive.<br>
<br>
All the 13.9 patch has done is put us back up <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> near</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> par with the other combat classes.<br>
<br>
I would hate to see us get so enthusiastic that we set ourselves up for a re-nerf.<br>
<br>
You can BET the other classes will be screaming bloody murder in a day or two, claiming we are now over-powered and similar bullshit.<br>
<br>
After all, they are used to having MA's be an easy kill, they are used to making us their bitch in PvP. They will whine up a storm if this is no longer possible, count on it.<br>
<br>
By all means let us be happy, by all means let us rejoice. But let us not do so so loudly that the 'com feels thay have any room to take back what has finally been restored to us.<br>
<br>
Finally, FINALLY, for the first time since beta, we have at least a chance to hold our own.<br>
<br>
<br>
